text: Ilaria Garzaro (born 29 September 1986 in Noventa Vicentina) is an Italian volleyball player. She played at the 2010 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2011 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Riviera Volley and Chateau d'Ax Urbino Volley. == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Italian volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Veneto
